---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Docker GitHub Actions CI/CD pro React | Frontend DevOps Průvodce"
  description="Docker a GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline pro React aplikace z nasazení O2 Czech Republic."
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      <a href="/de/" class="transition hover:text-accent">Startseite</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <a href="/de/vocabulary" class="transition hover:text-accent">Wortschatz</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <span class="text-slate-200">Docker + GitHub Actions CI/CD</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">DevOps a Nasazení</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Docker + GitHub Actions CI/CD</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Automatizované deployment pipelines pro React aplikace</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 shadow-card">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-100">
        <strong class="text-white">Definition:</strong> Automatizované deployment pipelines využívající Docker kontejnerizaci a GitHub Actions pro kontinuální integraci a doručování React aplikací.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Komponenty CI/CD Pipeline</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Docker multi-stage builds:</strong> Optimalizované container images s minimální velikostí</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">GitHub Actions workflows:</strong> Automatizované testování a nasazení při každém push</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Quality gates:</strong> ESLint, Prettier, unit testy, E2E testy musí projít</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Performance budgets:</strong> Kontroly velikosti bundle zabraňují regresím</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-accent">Případová Studie</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Reálná Implementace: O2 Czech Republic</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        <strong class="text-white">O2 Service Workbench</strong> používá Docker images s GitHub Actions spouštějícími Playwright testy, kontroly velikosti bundle a automatizované nasazení do staging/produkčních prostředí.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Související Wortschatz</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/de/vocabulary/playwright-testing" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">Playwright Testing</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">E2E testy v CI/CD pipeline</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/de/vocabulary/enterprise-react-developer" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">Enterprise React Developer</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">DevOps dovednosti pro frontend vývojáře</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 text-center shadow-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Potřebujete DevOps Nastavení?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-200">Konfiguruji Docker a CI/CD pipelines pro React aplikace.</p>
      <a href="mailto:marekdolnicek@gmail.com" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-ink shadow-card transition hover:bg-accentMuted">Kontaktujte mě</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
